Ultimate Talkie patch data

SCUMMKit includes minimal patch/table data from the original Monkey Island
Ultimate Talkie Edition builders by LogicDeLuxe:

- third_party/ultimate-talkie/mi1/patch10.000
- third_party/ultimate-talkie/mi1/patch10.001
- third_party/ultimate-talkie/mi1/monster.tbl
- third_party/ultimate-talkie/mi2/patch02.000
- third_party/ultimate-talkie/mi2/patch02.001
- third_party/ultimate-talkie/mi2/monster.tbl

These files are used with permission from the original patch author. Preserve
the original patch credit and license terms in licenses/original_ute_builder.txt.
They are third-party patch data, not MIT-licensed SCUMMKit source code. They are
provided for building local ScummVM-compatible outputs from legally owned game
installs. Do not redistribute generated game output or commercial game assets.
